*Predlog* da se svako veče organizuje neko druženje. (The suggestion that a gathering is organized every evening.)

*Predlogom* se predviđa da će svi biti obavešteni u roku od nedelju dana. (It is proposed that everyone will be informed within a week.)

*Predložio* je da se održi skup o ovoj temi. (He proposed that a meeting on this topic be held.)

*Predloženi* program je veoma interesantan. (The proposed program is very interesting.)

*Predložio* je da se napravi zajednički dogovor. (He proposed that an agreement be reached.)